{
  "name": "fix-graph-impact-type-alias-deps",
  "createdAt": "2026-05-05T05:17:22.047Z",
  "description": "Fix missing impact edges when symbols are referenced through type aliases and registry indirection (e.g. ArtifactParserRegistry -> ArtifactParser). Adds graph-derivation fingerprint for staleness detection, config-relative file selector resolution, and removes the confusing --changes flag from graph impact. Updates 8 specs across code-graph, CLI, and skills packages.",
